data.description: HIGHLY MOTIVATED SELLER. ***** USDA LOAN HOUSE QUALIFIES 100% FINANCING, CASH, CONVENTIONAL OR FHA LOAN. Short Term Rental allowed*****. Buyer to assume remainder balance of solar panels.  These solar panels are transferable and new owner must meet transfer term.  Two-Story Home with Energy-Efficient Features and Two Master Bedrooms.  This beautiful two-story home boasts two Master Suites, one located on the first floor and a second one in the second floor with a lounge area large enough for an office/ or a nursery. The two secondary bedrooms and den space located on the first floor. The kitchen has light color cabinet and stainless steel appliances all included with the house. For your additional peace of mind this home features had wired security cameras  pointing in all directions covering all the exterior of the home. The community has LOW Hoa at $77.24 a month and it includes a pool and a covered playground for your enjoyment. The location of this community is desirable with supermarkets, restaurants and the attractions just minutes away.
